<li>Palmer, Robert (1995). <i>Rock &amp; Roll: An Unruly History.</i> New York: Harmony Books. 325 pages. <a href="Special_BookSources/0517700506" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-517-70050-6</a>. <a href="Robert_Palmer_(writer)" title="Robert Palmer (writer)">Robert Palmer (writer)</a>.</li>
</ul>
